title: Everything to Know About Climate Activist Group Just Stop Oil
description: Just Stop Oil is the British activist group behind viral stunts. The group is opposed to new U.K. fossil fuel projects.

title: Weight Loss Drug Wegovy Can Also Reduce Risk of Serious Heart Events, Study Shows

title: Police Monitor Major Pro-Palestinian March in London as Counter-Protesters Are Arrested

title: Gaza’s Main Hospital Goes Dark Amid Intense Fighting

title: ‘They Are Behaving in a Fascist Way:’ An Israeli-Arab Lawmaker on the Stifling of Anti-War Voices

title: Hollywood Actors Union Board Approves Strike-Ending Deal as Leaders Tout Gains
